subject: Re: Very interesting New Files and some old uploaded as Mp3's

full_text:
Those are some good files you've collected Ralph.  Especially the one
that says, "you're now prepared for contact by telephone."  That one
is very clear to me.  

Does that mean they are going to start calling?  If they ever want to
call me, they better be listed because I screen all my calls. 
Something like Spirit Realm or Steve's Spirit on the caller i.d. is
all I need.  I'd definitely answer then. 

Jeremy
